      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MORNING DAYLIGHT (3) is a progressive type who recorded her 8th career win last time out (22.28) at this track. Has never missed the frame at the trip from seven starts. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Looks to have an edge on most of these. PREMIER STATUS (1) is a quick dog who thrives over the short dashes. Found it a bit far latest when finished fifth over 401m at Richmond (23.41) in a Grade 4/5 but is better suited back in trip here. Goes very well at the journey winning four races. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. NAUGHTY ZESTA (2) has been a little hard to follow, missing the frame last time but was a Grade 5 winner three starts ago and has drawn 2 where he has two wins. Well placed here and should do much better. SMART MINX (8) justified the favourite's tag last time and is in the mix again.",
